'''Mary Elizabeth Burroughs''' is a ''[[Star Wars]]'' fan who designed the [[Scalt]] in the [[Design An Alien]] contest held in the ''[[Star Wars Galaxy Magazine]]s''. The entry was given an honorable mention in the under 16 years old category. She was 14 at the time her entry was published. She is now a writer of speculative fiction and has attended the Clarion Science Fiction & Fantasy Writers' Workshop at UC, San Diego in 2008.

